>

> any case, especially wtih your only known associate being the SPIDER who has
> hardly proven himself worthy of any attention regardless?"

<NEW>

There was a grunt of surprise from ANTAGONY, "Me, and the spider bot
here?" She hooked a dismiisive thumb at TARANTULUS. "Don't make me
laugh."

"Not worthy of any attention?!?" Sputtered TARANTULUS. "I warn you,
you are useful to me, but I will terminate you if you continue to anoy
me!"

He looked at ANTAGONY, "And you, I will disseect you into componant
parts and take what information I need."

SKY SHADOW frowned, "You don't have the power to take on all of us,
probrably not even one of us." He held out his weapon directing it at
TARANTULUS as he alerted the other FUZORS to enter the chamber.

TARANTULUS laughed, "I have not been idle while this ship sat here
unused." He gestured languidly at the room itself. "Ship, erect a
level 5 force shield around this chamber and activate standard safety
measures for myself." he said as he now gestured at them.

"ACKNOWLEDGED." a deep voice intoned all around them and Immedietly a
bluish purple energy field snapped into place around the room and the
main doors locked. At the same time larger gun units extended from the
cieling and oriented on SKYSHADOW, DINOBOT and ANTAGONY.

"DECEPTICON AND PREDACON SIGNATURE DETECTED." The ship intoned.

"What now?" TARANTULUS said quarrilously. He looked at his screen.
"Ahh it is Cryotek returning after all, and whom does he have with him
. . ahhhh the Horrocons."

He rubbed his hands together, "more visitors." he sat back in his
chair as he looked at the trio, "But what to do with you . .. . hmmmm
. . . "

(TAG)

- Preston
